GxEPD2_3C library includes Adafruit_GFX, which needs Adadruit_BusIO library to work,
so mentioned libraries are for GxEPD2_213_Z98c display. 
Connection should be established via pins:

ESP32   |   Display
--------------------  
    5   |   CS
    17  |   DC
    16  |   RESET
    4   |   BUSY

-Avram K